stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> CatchingUp: 新副本/重启副本
    CatchingUp --> SyncStateSet: maxOffset >= confirmOffset\n且已进入当前 Epoch
    SyncStateSet --> Lagging: 超时未追上或连接丢失
    Lagging --> Outside: Controller 提交收缩
    Outside --> CatchingUp: 重新连接并追赶
    SyncStateSet --> Candidate: 当前 Master 故障
    Candidate --> NewMaster: Controller 选举并 masterEpoch+1
    NewMaster --> SyncStateSet: 新集合初始仅含新 Master
